::Triggerhappy/Skullgrin/Jume/Whee::

&quot;Okay, listen up.  We&#39;re gonna need a diversion, to distract them a small
bit.  Whee, Jume, and Skullgrin, you guys attack that area, and wait until
they come out.  Actually, Skullgrin, you attack that other area, so they
have two areas to deal with, that side and that side.  Then, Blindfear, I
want you to attack the entrance.  Meanwhile, I&#39;ll be at the back, and I&#39;ll
be calling in for reinforcements from the base!  And, just keep attacking
until my word.  Oh, Skullgrin, Jume and Whee, when your attacking, slowly
take your attack to the entrance, so then you&#39;ll all be at the entrance
attacking.  It may seem like they outnumber you, but in fact, once the
reinforcements arrive, we&#39;ll do fine.  Then, we must move our way inside the
base!  Some Decepticons will stay out here and battle these guys, and some
others will start rampaging inside.  Now, let&#39;s do it.  Wait till I get
where I need to be.&quot;

Triggerhappy went behind the base.

&quot;Now!&quot;  he said through comm, &quot;Blindfear, attack front, Jume, Whee and
Skullgrin, attack the sides!&quot;

Skullgrin nodded, and JUme and Whee did also.  Jume and Whee went to their
issued side, and Skullgrin went to his.  Skullgrin fired some shots at the
base.  Jume and Whee also fired their weapons at it.  Triggerhappy was ready
to ask for reinforcements.  He decided to send a message to the whole Dark
Avian(technology, gotta love it!).

&quot;All Decepticons, I repeat, all Decepticons!  We are carrying out
infiltration of Maximal City!  The ones here right now are Skullgrin,
Blindfear, Jume, and Whee!  I request that reinforcements arrive at my
location and attack as quick as possible!!!!!  Over!&quot; Triggerhappy said loud
and clear.
